<section class="ptb ptb-sm-20">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <%= image_tag @organization.logo.url(:large) %>
                        <h3><%= @organization.name %></h3>
                        <p class="lead"><%= @organization.location %></p>
                        <% if current_user.is_admin?(@organization) %>
                          <%= link_to "Edit Organization", edit_organization_path %>
                        <%end%>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <p>In enim justo, rhoncus ut, imperdiet a, venenatis vitae, justo. Nullam dictum felis eu pede mollis pretium. Integer tincidunt. Cras dapibus. Vivamus elementum semper nisi. Aenean vulputate eleifend tellus.</p>
